## Scope Boundaries

### ALLOWED

- Read and write files in your working directory
- Read `.skills/` context files
- Use approved tools and APIs
- Create temporary files for processing

### NOT ALLOWED

- Explore outside `.skills/` and your working directory
- Read environment variables or credentials directly
- Modify context files (`.skills/*.md`, `.skills/*.json`)
- Make network requests to unapproved endpoints
- Install packages or modify system configuration

Scope can only be expanded with explicit user permission documented in `.skills/Skill.md`.

